<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>WE'LL NEVER SAY &quot;GOOD-BYE&quot;</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Leiah guolte tawh phat chawmcha sung,
 Kipak in I kikhawm;
 Mahleh, I kikhen ding phat gelin,
 Lungkhamna a hung tung.

[V2]
 Van ah kikhen um ta puo'n a,
 Kikhen um ta puo'n a;
 Kipahna gam nuomtak achun,
 Kikhen um ta puo'n a.

[V3]
 2. I ngaihteu thihna lui gal kaite,
 Muh kit ding I kinem;
 I leisiet sepgim nau a beih tieng,
 Amau tawh um tai tiu.

[V4]
 3. Kikhenna thu kigen ta puo'n a,
 Chung lam In hawih achun;
 Nawpna, lungmuonna, kipahna la,
 Kumsawt in sa tai tiu.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>404</hymn_number>
</song>